A directory for testing c++ client <-- thrift --> java server
Use the following classpaths:
~/thrift-0.9.2/lib/java/build/libthrift-0.9.2.jar:
~/thrift-0.9.2/lib/java/build/lib/slf4j-api-1.5.8.jar:
~/thrifttests:
~/javatests:
~/thrifttests/gen-java/tutorial:
~/thrift-0.9.2/lib/java/build/lib/slf4j-log4j12-1.5.8.jar:
~/thrift-0.9.2/lib/java/build/lib/log4j-1.2.14.jar

Note: this is just a work-in-progress. I'm planning to put the 
final version in ~/sirius/sirius-application/question-answer/openephyra-thrift/
